## üß∏ 1. THE "LOLI-LAWYER" EXPLAINER (tl;dr)
listen, i know legal documents are usually a wall of boring gray text that makes you want to close the tab. but this one is different. this is the **GNU General Public License v3.0**, but with a crochet soul. 

basically, i spent countless hours in **notepad++** fighting "trash white" (#ffffff) and making sure the **comic sans** looked exactly like a pro-gamer-stitch. i did the hard work so you don't have to. in exchange, i only ask for one thing: **don't be a corporate gatekeeper.**

