## üñãÔ∏è 2. YOUR RIGHTS (THE GOOD STUFF)
under this license, you have the "freedom to stitch." this means:

* **FREEDOM TO SHARE**: you can send this file to your friends, your family, your crochet group, or a random person on the internet. spread the ivory vibes. üç¶
* **FREEDOM TO MODIFY**: if you think a specific button should be a different shade of almond, go for it! change the code, add your own stitches, and make it yours.
* **FREEDOM TO RE-DISTRIBUTE**: if you make a "strawberry cream" or "mint cream" version based on my code, you are allowed to share it! just make sure you give me credit for the original sturdy-stitch base.

