## üèÅ 5. THE ULTIMATUM ON "TRASH"
even though this is a legal GPL-3.0 document, i am adding a **social contract** to it. 

if you use this license to create a fork of **cream**, you are legally (spiritually) obligated to never use `#ffffff` for a background color. if i find out you've turned this beautiful ivory parchment into a blinding white flashbang, the crochet community (and me) will be very disappointed.

